Program: Outlook
Title: Spurious Connections to Donald Trump
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csvr1c
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 4 Dec 2017
John Di Domenico makes a living impersonating Donald Trump. He has spent years studying the American president and even made an appearance at his 55th birthday. Jill Dodd was an American model when she met billionaire Adnan Khashoggi and was invited onto his superyacht which was later sold to Donald Trump. (Photo: US billionaire Donald Trump's yacht 'Trump Princess' pictured in 1991. It was originally built as 'Nabila' for Saudi billionaire Adnan Khashoggi. Credit: JACQUES SOFFER/AFP/Getty Images) Show less